headline: 5 Retirement Income Tips Once Your Portfolio Reaches $500,000
summary: Hitting the $500,000 portfolio milestone is a big deal that deserves a nice pat on the back. That said, if you’re gearing up for an earlier retirement (let’s say in your 50s), things could get a bit more challenging if you’re not expecting social security benefits to be coming your way any time soon. headline: Barclays Maintains Equal-Weight on Crown Castle, Lowers Price Target to $91
summary: Barclays  analyst Brendan Lynch   maintains Crown Castle (NYSE:CCI) with a Equal-Weight and lowers the price target from $101 to $91.
